Bajar ScaLAPACK installer de http://www.netlib.org/scalapack/

Instalar paquetes:
	libblas3gf
	libblas-dev
	liblapack3gf
	liblapack-dev
	openmpi-bin
	libopenmpi1.3
	libopenmpi-dev

En la carpeta de ScaLAPACK installer:
	./setup.py --mpiincdir=/usr/lib/openmpi/include/ --downblas --lapacklib=/usr/lib/liblapack.so.3gf --blaslib=/usr/lib/libblas.so.3gf
